    "The statistics of the CSE dataset are shown in Table 1.",
    "Implementation detailsIn our implementation, we used RoBERTa-large [45] as the nonsensical concept detector.",
    "For all LLMs used in the experiments, the following parameters were consistently applied: top_k set to 10, temperature set to 0.1 and top_p set to 0.95.",
    "These hyper-parameters help control the diversity of generated outputs while maintaining coherence in the explanations.",
    "The experiments were run on a server equipped with two NVIDIA A100 GPUs, each with 80GB of GPU memory."
